hadiths[51]{hadithnumber,text}:
1619,"kaha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! kon sa amal ( ajr o sawab mein) jihad key barabar hai? aap ney farmaya : '' tum log uski taqat nahin rakhtey '' , Sahaba ney do ya teen martaba aap key samney yehi sawal dohraaya, aap har martaba kehtey : '' tum log iski taqat nahin rakhtey'', teesri martaba aap ney farmaya : ''Allah key raastey mein jihad karney waley ki misal us namazi aur rozeydaar ki hai jo namaz aur rozey sey nahin rukta (ye dono amal musalsal karta hi chala jata ( hai yahan tak ke Allah ki raah ka Mujahid wapis aa jaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Hurera key wastey sey marfoo tariqa sey aai hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein shifaa , Abdullah bin Habshi , abu-Musa , abu-Saeed , Umme Malik Behaz ye aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1620,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : Allah key rastey mein jihad karney waley ka zaamin main hun, agar main uski rooh qabz karun to usko jannat ka waris banaunga, aur agar main usey (uskey ghar) wapis bhejun to ajr ya ghanimat key sath wapis bhejunga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey sahih gharib hai."
1621,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' har maiyat key amal ka silsila band kar diya jata hai siwaye us shakhs key jo Allah key raastey mein sarhad ki pasbani kartey huye marey , to uska amal qiyamat key din tak badhaya jata rahega aur wo qabr key fitney sey maamun rahega , mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye bhi farmatey huye suna : Mujahid wo hai jo apney nafs sey jihad kerey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Fazala ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aqba bin Aamir aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1622,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs jihad kartey waqt eik din ka roza rakhey Allah Taala usey sattar saal ki masafat tak jahannam sey door kerega '' padhi. . Urwa bin Zuber aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar mein sey eik ney ''sattar baras'' kaha hai aur doosrey ney'' chaalis baras''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- Raavi Abul ka naam Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Naufal Asadi madni hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed, Anas, Aqba bin Aamir aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1623,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raahe-jihad mein koi banda eik din bhi roza rakhta hai to wo din uskey chehrey sey sattar saal ki masafat tak jahannam ki aag ko door kar dega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1624,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jihad mein jo shakhs eik din roza rakhega Allah Taala uskey aur aag key darmiyan isi tarah ki eik khandaq bana dega jaisi zamin o aasman key darmiyan hai ''. ye hadees abu-Umama ki riwayat sey gharib hai.
1625,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Allah key raastey ( jihad ( mein kuch kharch kya uskey liye saat so guna (sawab) likh liya gaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, is hadees ko hum Rukein bin Rabee hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1626,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sawal kya : kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : '' Allah key raastey mein) kisi Mujahid ko) ghulam ka Atiya dena ya ( mujahideen key liye ( khemey ka saya karna, ya Allah key raastey mein jawan oontni dena''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muawiya bin Saleh sey ye hadees mursal tariqa sey bhi aai hai, 2- baaz asnaad ( turq ( mein Zaid (bin Hubab) ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai, is hadees ko Waleed bin Jameel ney Qasim abu-Abdur-Rehman sey , Qasim ney abu-Umama sey , aur abu-Umama ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, hum sey is hadees ko Ziyad bin Ayub ney bayan kya hai."
1627,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jihad mein) mujahideen key liye ( khemey ka saya karna, khaadim ka Atiya dena aur jawan oontni dena sab sey afzal o behtar sadqa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- merey nazdik ye Muawiya bin Saleh ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
1628,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ka saman safar tayyar kya haqiqat mein usney jihad kya aur jisney ghaazi key ehal o ayaal mein uski jaa-nasheeni ki) uskey ehal o ayaal ki khabargiri ki) haqiqat mein usney jihad kya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, ye dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai."
1629,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi Mujahid ka saman safar tayyar kya, ya uskey ghar waley ki khabargiri ki haqiqat mein usney jihad kya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1630,Zaid bin Khalid johni sey usi jaisi hadees marvi hai.
1631,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi Mujahid ka samane-safar tayyar kya haqiqat mein usney jihad kya aur jisney ghaazi key ghar waley ki khabargiri ki haqiqat mein usney jihad kya''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1632,"main Juma key liye ja raha tha ke mujhey Abaya bin Rifaa bin Raafey miley , unhoney kaha : khush ho jaao , tumharey ye qadam Allah key raastey mein hain, mainey abu-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis key dono pair Allah key raastey mein ghubar aalud hon , unhen jahannam ki aag nahin chu sakti ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- abu-Abbas ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin jabr hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar aur eik doosrey Sabab sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1633,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah key dar sey roney wala jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga yahan tak ke doodh than mein wapis lot jaey, (aur ye muhal hai) aur jihad ka ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan eik sath jama nahin hongey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1634,"Kaab bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) ! hum sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees bayan kijiye aur kami ziyadti sey mohtaat rahiye, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jo Islam mein boodha ho jaey, to qiyamat key din ye uskey liye Noor bin kar aayega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Fazala bin Ubaid aur Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Kaab bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko Aamash ney isi tarah Amr bin Murra sey riwayat ki hai, ye hadees mansoor sey bhi aai hai, unhoney Salim bin abi ja'ad sey riwayat ki hai, unhoney Salim aur Kaab bin Murra key darmiyan sanad main eik aadmi ko dakhil kya hai, 3- Kaab bin Murra ko kabhi Kaab bin Murra aur Murra bin Kaab Behzi bhi kaha gaya hai, unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain."
1635,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein boodha ho jaaey qiyamat key din uskey liye eik Noor hoga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
1636,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ghodey ki peshani mein qiyamat tak key liye khair bandhi hui hai, ghodey teen tarah key hotey hain : eik ghoda wo hai jo aadmi key liye baaise-ajr hai, eik wo ghoda hai jo aadmi ki (izzat o waqar) key liye parda poshi ka baais hai, aur eik ghoda wo hai jo aadmi key liye baaise-gunah hai, wo aadmi jiskey liye ghoda baaise-ajr hai wo aisa shakhs hai jo us ko jihad key liye rakhta hai, aur usi key liye tayyar karta hai, ye ghoda us shakhs key liye baaise-ajr hai, uskey pet mein jo chiz ( khurak ( bhi jati hai Allah Taala uskey liye ajr o sawab likh deta hai'' , is hadees main eik qissey ka zikr hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - Malik bin Anas ney b-tareeq : (زيد بن أسلم an أبي صالح an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
1637,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala eik teer ki wajeh sey teen aadmiyon ko jannat mein dakhil kerega : teer bananey waley ko jo banatey waqt sawab ki niyat rakhta ho, teer andaz ko aur teer deney waley ko '' , aap ney farmaya : '' teer andazi karo aur sawari seekho , tumhara teer andazi karna merey nazdik tumharey sawari karney sey ziyada pasandida hai, har wo chiz jis sey musalman khelta hai batil hai siwaye kamaan sey uska teerandazi karna, ghodey ko tarbiyat dena aur apni biwi key sath khelna, ye teeno cheezen uskey liye durust hain''."
1638,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : '' jisney Allah ki raah main eik teer maara , wo ( sawab mein) eik ghulam azad karney key barabar hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- Abu-Najeeh ka naam Amr bin Abasa Salma hai, 3- Abdullah bin Azraq sey murad Abdullah bin Zaid hain."
1639,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''do aakhon ko jahannam ki aag nahin chhueygi : eik wo aankh jo Allah key dar sey tar hui ho aur eik wo aankh jisney raahe-jihad mein pehra detey huye raat guzaari ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Shuaib bin Ruzeq hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usman aur Abu Rehana Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1640,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ki raah mein shahadat ( shaheed key liye (har gunah ka kaffara bin jati hai, Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : ''siwaye qarz key'', Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bhi farmaya : '' siwaye qarz key '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum is hadees ko abi bakar ki riwayat sey sirf isi Shekh (yani Yahya bin Talha ( key wastey sey jantey hain, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney la-ilmi ka izhar kya aur kaha : mera khayal hai Yahya bin Talha ney Humed ki hadees bayan karna chahi jisko unhoney Anas sey, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''shaheed key ilawa koi aisa jannati nahin hai jo duniya ki taraf lotna chahey'', padhi. 2- is bab mein Kaab bin Ajra, Jabir, Abu-Hurera aur abu-Qatada sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1641,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' shuda ki roohen ( jannat mein) sabz (harey) parindon ki shakal mein hain, jo jannat key phalon ya darakhton sey khati charti hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1642,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey ooper un teen ashkhaas ko pesh kya gaya jo jannat mein sab sey pehley jaeyngey : eik shaheed , doosra haram sey door rehney wala aur namunasib maamlon sey bachney wala , teesra wo ghulam jo achi tarah Allah ki ibadat baja laye aur apney mallikon key liye khair chahey ya unkey huquq baja laye''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1643,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' marney wala koi aisa banda nahin hai jis key liye Allah key paas sawab ho aur wo duniya ki taraf duniya aur duniya mein jo kuch hai uski khatir lotna chahta ho. siwaye shaheed key , isliye ke wo shahadat ka maqam o martaba dekh chuka hai, chunanche wo chahta hai ke duniya ki taraf lot jaey aur dobara shaheed ho ( kar aaye ( ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1644,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''shaheed chaar tarah key hain : pehla wo achchhey eman wala momin jo dushman sey muqable aur Allah sey kiye gaey wade ko sach kar dikhaye yahan tak ke shaheed ho jaey, yehi wo shakhs hai jiski taraf qiyamat key din log is tarah aankhen utha kar dekhengey aur (Raavi Fazala bin Ubaid ney iski kaifiyat ko bayan karney key liye kaha ( apna sar uthaya yahan tak ke topi (sar sey) gir gaee.''  Raavi Abu Yazeed Khaulaani kehtey hain : mujhey nahin malum Fazala ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki topi murad li ya Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki, aap ney farmaya : ''doosra wo achchhey eman wala momin jo dushman ka muqabla is tarah karey to un buzdili ki wajeh sey uski jild ( khaal ( « طلح » (eik bada khaardaar darkht ( key kaatey sey zakhmi ho gaee ho, peechey sey (eik anjan) teer aa kar usey lagey aur maar daley, ye doosrey darje mein hai, teesra wo momin jo nek amal key sath bura amal bhi karey, jab dushman sey muqabla karey to Allah sey kiye gaey wade ko sach kar dikhaye ( yani bahaaduri sey ladtaa rahey ( yahan tak ke shaheed ho jaey, ye teesrey darje mein hai, chotha wo momin shakhs jo apney nafs par zulm karey ( yani kasrate-gunah ki wajeh sey , aur bahaaduri sey ladtaa rahey ( yahan tak ke shaheed ho jaey, ye chauthey darje mein hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ata bin Dinar hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : ye hadees Saeed bin Abi Ayub ney Ata bin Dinar sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney Khulaan key Mashaaikh sey riwayat ki hai is mein unhoney Abu Yazeed ka zikr nahin kiya, aur Ata bin Dinar ney kaha : (ke is hadees mein) kuchh harj nahin hai."
1645,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Umme Haram binte Milhaan key ghar jab bhi jatey , wo aap ko khana khilatin, Umme Haram (Raziallahu Anha) Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) key nikah mein thin, eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam in key paas gaey to unhoney aap ko khana khilaya aur aap key sar mein juein dekhney beth gaeen , aap so gaey, phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bedaar huye to hans rahey they, Umme Haram (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ko kya chiz hansa rahi hai? aap ney ( jawab mein) farmaya : '' merey samney meri ummat key kuchh mujahideen pesh kiye gaey, wo us samandar key seene par sawar they, takhton par bethey huye badshah lagtey they.'' Raavi ko shak hai ke aap ney (ملوك على الأسرة) kaha , ya (مثل الملوك على الأسرة) mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah sey dua kar dijiye ki Allah mujhey bhi un logon mein kar dey , chunanche aap ney unkey liye dua farmaee, aap phir apna sar rakh kar so gaey, phir hanstey huye bedaar huye, mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ko kya chiz hansa rahi hai? farmaya : ''merey samney meri ummat key kuchh log Allah key raastey mein jihad kartey huye pesh kiye gaey.''  aap ney isi tarah farmaya jaisey is sey pehley farmaya tha, mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah sey dua kar dijiye ki mujhey un logon mein kar dey , aap ney farmaya : ''tum (samandar mein) pehley (jihad karney) waley logon mein sey ho.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan Raziallahu anhuma key zamane mein Umme Haram (Raziallahu Anha) samandari safar par (eik jihad mein) niklin to wo samandar sey nikaltey waqt apni sawari sey gir gaeen aur halak ho gaeen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Umme Haram binte Milhaan , Umme Sulem ki behan aur Anas bin Malik ki khaala hain, (aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nanihaal mein sey qaribi rishte-daar thin)."
1646,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : eik aadmi izhar shuja'at (bahaaduri) key liye ladtaa hai, doosra hamiyat ki wajeh sey ladtaa hai, teesra riyaakaari key liye ladtaa hai, in mein sey Allah key raastey mein kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah key kalime ki sarbulandi key liye jihad kerey. wo Allah key raastey mein hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1647,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''amal ka daromadar niyat par hai, aadmi ko wohi milega jiski usney niyat ki, chunanche jiski hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool key liye hogi usi ki hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool key liye maana jaeygi aur jisney husoole duniya ya kisi aurat sey shaadi karney key liye hijrat ki hogi to uski hijrat usi key liye hogi jis key liye usney hijrat ki.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Malik bin Anas , Sufiyan Sory aur kaee aimma  ney isey Yahya bin Saeed sey riwayat kiya hai, hum isey sirf Yahya bin Saeed Ansari hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi kehtey hain : hamein is hadees ko har baab mein rakhna chahiye."
1648,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raahe jihad ki eik subah duniya aur duniya ki sari chizon sey behtar hai aur jannat ki eik kodey padhi. ki jagah duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , abu-Ayyub aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1649,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jihad ki eik subah ya eik Sham duniya aur is mein jo kuchh hai us sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- jise abu-Haazim ney Sehal bin Saad sey riwayat ki hai wo abu-Haazim Zahid hain, Madina key rehney waley hain aur unka naam Salma bin Dinar hai, aur ye abu-Haazim jinhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai ye abu-Haazim Ashjai hain, koofa key rehney waley inka naam Salman hai aur ye Azza Ashjaiyya key azad karda ghulam hain."
1650,"Sahaba mein sey eik aadmi kisi pahadi ki ghaati sey guzra jis mein meethey pani ka eik chhota sa chashma tha, wo jagah aur chashma apni latafat ki wajeh sey isey bahut pasand aaya , usney kaha (socha) : kaash! main logon sey alag thalag ho kar is ghaati mein qiyam pazeer ho jata, lekin main aisa hergiz nahin karunga yahan tak ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ijazat talab kar lun usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey iska tazkira kiya, aap ney farmaya : ''aisa na karo, isliye ke tum mein sey kisi ka Allah key raastey mein khade rehna apney ghar mein sattar saal namaz padhtey rehney sey behtar hai, kya tum log nahin chahtey ho ke Allah tumharey gunahon ko bakhsh dey aur tum ko jannat mein dakhil kar dey? Allah ki raah mein jihad karo, jisney Allah ki raah mein do martaba doodh dohney key darmiyan key waqfa key barabar jihad kiya uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1651,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''raahe-jihad ki eik subah ya eik Sham sari duniya sey behtar hai, aur tum mein sey kisi ki kamaan ya haath key barabar jannat ki jagah duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai padhi. , agar jannat ki aurton mein sey koi aurat zamin ki taraf nikal aaye to zamin aur aasman key darmiyan ki sari cheezen roshan ho jaeyn aur khushbu sey bhar jaeyn aur uskey sar ka dupatta duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
1652,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tum logon ko sab sey behtar aadmi key barey mein na bata dun? ye wo aadmi hai jo Allah ki raah mein apney ghodey ki lagaam pakdey rahey, kya main tum logon ko us aadmi key barey mein na bata dun jo martabe mein iskey baad hai? ye wo aadmi hai jo logon sey alag ho kar apni bakriyon key darmiyan reh kar Allah ka haq ada karta rahey. kya main tum ko bad-tareen aadmi key barey mein na bata dun? ye wo aadmi hai jis sey Allah ka wasta dey kar manga jaey aur wo na dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey marfoo tariqa sey aai hai."
1653,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs sachey dil sey shahadat ki dua maangey to Allah Taala usey shuda key martabey tak pahuncha dega agar-che wo apney bistar hi par kyon na marey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sehal bin Hanif ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Shureh ki hi riwayat sey jantey hain, is hadees ko Abdur-Rehman bin Shureh sey Abdullah bin Saleh ney bhi riwayat kiya hai, Abdur-Rehman bin Shureh ki kunniyat Abu-Shuraih hai aur wo sikandariya key rehney waley hain. 2- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1654,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs sachey dil sey Allah ki raah mein qatl honey ki dua maangey to Allah Taala usey shahadat ka sawab dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1655,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen aadmiyon ki madad Allah key nazdik Sabit hai padhi. eik Allah ki raah mein jihad karney wala , doosra wo makatib ghulam jo zare-kitabat ada karna chahta ho, aur teesra wo shaadi karney wala jo paak-daamni hasil karna chahta ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1656,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ki raah mein jo bhi zakhmi hoga. aur Allah khub janta hai jo uski raah mein zakhmi hota hai.  qiyamat key din is tarah aayega ke khoon key rang mein ranga huwa hoga aur khushbu mushk ki hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai.
1657,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo musalman Allah ki raah mein oontni key do martaba doodh dohney key darmiyani waqfe key barabar jihad karey uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee, aur jis shakhs ko Allah ki raah mein koi zakham lagey ya chot aaye wo qiyamat key din is tarah aayega ke uska zakham duniya key zakham sey kahin bada hoga, rang uska za'fraan ka hoga aur khushbu mushk ki hogi.''"
1658,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai, ya kon sa amal sab sey behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : '' Allah aur uskey Rasool par eman lana.''  puchha gaya : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : ''jihad , wo neki ka kohaan hai.'' puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! phir kon? aap ney farmaya : ''Hajje-Mabroor (maqbool).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey marfoo tariqa sey kaee sanadon sey aai hai."
1659,"Mainey dushmanon ki mojudgi mein apney baap ko kehtey huye suna : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak jannat key darwazey talwaaron ki chhaoon mein hain.''  qom mein sey eik bikhre hue haiyat waley shakhs ney puchha : kya aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isko bayan kartey huye suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan , chunanche wo aadmi lot kar apney sathiyon key paas gaya aur bola : main tum sab ko salam karta hun, phir usney apni talwaar ki niyaam tod diya aur us sey ladaai karta raha yahan tak ke wo shaheed ho gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Jaafar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) Zab'ee ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1660,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : kon aadmi afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : '' wo shakhs jo Allah key raastey mein jihad karta hai.''  Sahaba ney puchha : phir kon? aap ney farmaya : '' phir wo momin jo kisi ghaati mein akela ho aur apney rab sey darey aur logon ko apney shar sey bachaey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1661,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shaheed key ilawa koi jannati aisa nahin hai jo duniya ki taraf lotna chahta ho wo duniya ki taraf lotna chahta hai, kehta hai : ( dil chahta hai ke) Allah ki raah mein das martaba qatl kiya jaaun , ye is wajeh sey ke wo us maqam ko dekh chuka hai jis sey Allah ney us ko nawaza hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1662,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1663,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah key nazdik shaheed key liye chhe inaamat hain. (1) khoon ka pehla qatra girney key sath hi uski maghfirat ho jati hai. (2) wo jannat main apni jagah dekh leta hai. (3) azabe qabr sey mehfooz rehta hai. (4) « فزع الأكبر » ( azeem ghabrahat waley din ( sey maamoon rahega. (5) uskey sar par izzat ka taaj rakha jaeyga jis ka eik yaqut duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai. (6) behttar (72) jannati hooron sey uski shaadi ki jaeygi, aur uskey sattar rishte-daaron key silsiley mein uski shafaat qubul ki jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1664,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah ki raah mein sarhad ki eik din ki pasbani karna duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai, tum mein sey kisi key kodey key barabar jannat ki jagah duniya aur duniya ki sari chizon sey behtar hai aur bandey ka Allah ki raah mein subah ya Sham key waqt chalna duniya aur uski sari chizon sey behtar hai.''"
1665,"Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) Shurehbil bin Samt key paas sey guzrey, wo apney « مرابط » (sarhad par pasbani ki jagah) mein they, un par aur unkey sathiyon par wahan rehna giraan guzar raha tha, Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ibne Samat? kya main tum sey wo hadees bayan na karun jisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna hai? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''Allah ki raah main eik din ki pasbani eik maah roze rakhney aur tahajjud padhney sey afzal hai, aap ney (afzal) ki bajaey kabhi  (khair) ( behtar hai) ka lafz kaha : aur jo shakhs is haalat mein wafat paa gaya, wo azabe-qabr sey mehfooz rahega aur qiyamat tak uska amal badhaya jaeyga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1666,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs jihad key kisi asar key baghair Allah Taala sey miley padhi. to wo us haal mein Allah sey milega ke uskey andar khalal (nuqs aur aeb) hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Waleed bin Muslim key wastey sey Ismail bin Raafey ki riwayat sey zaeef hai, baaz muhaddeseen ney Ismail bin Raafey ki tazeef ki hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Ismail bharosemand hain, maqaribul hadees hain. 2- ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi Abu-Hurera key wastey sey marfoo tareeq sey aai hai. 3- Salman ki hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai. Muhammad bin Munkadir ney Salman ko nahin paya hai. ye hadees :(عن أيوب بن موسى an مكحول an شرحبيل بن السمط an سلمان an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1667,"Mainey member par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna : mainey tum logon sey eik hadees chhupa li thi jisey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna hai is dar ki wajeh sey ke tum mujh sey juda ho jaaogey padhi. phir meri samajh mein aaya ke main tum logon sey isey bayan kar dun taake har aadmi apney liye wohi chiz ikhtiyar karey jo uski samajh mein aaye, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''Allah ki raah main eik din sarhad ki pasbani karna dusri jagahon key eik hazar din ki pasbani sey behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1668,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shaheed ko qatl sey sirf itni hi takleef hoti hai jitni takleef tum mein sey kisi ko chutki leney sey hoti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
1669,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ko do qatron aur do nishaniyon sey ziyada koi chiz mehbub nahin hai : aansu ka eik qatra jo Allah key khof ki wajeh sey nikley aur doosra khoon ka wo qatra jo Allah key raaste mein bahey, do nishaniyon mein sey eik nishani wo hai jo Allah ki raah mein lagey aur dusri nishani wo hai jo Allah key faraaiz mein sey kisi fariza ki adaegi ki haalat mein lagey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
